(76, 0, 76, NULL, NULL, 'Possible CSRF BackEnd  Smart Search Indexer ', '<p>not important bug but its bug</p>\n\n<p>also if reload page often it may create issues </p>\n\n<p>http://localhost/joomla25/administrator/index.php?option=com_finder&amp;view=indexer&amp;tmpl=component</p>\n\n<p>Version 2.5.0_Beta1</p>', 3, 0, 1, '2012-01-06 15:00:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-01-06 15:01:00', NULL),
