(80, 0, 80, NULL, NULL, 'Improve handling of edit.state permissions to address a number of contex...', '<p>Improve handling of edit.state permissions to address a number of contexts and issues.<br><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=27216">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=27216</a><br><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=25853">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=25853</a></p>\n\n<p>This includes a platform change that has a separate pull request but it is really necessary for testing the other changes.</p>\n\n<p><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/issues/722" class="issue-link" title="Fix category field to correctly manage edit.state permissions in combina...">joomla/joomla-platform#722</a></p>\n\n<p>This is a complex issue with testing scenarios described in each of the related tracker issues. </p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-01-07 23:18:49', '2012-01-18 16:01:17', '2012-01-18 16:01:17', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/80.diff'),
