(151, 0, 151, NULL, NULL, 'Email cloak resets body content when loaded with AJAX', '<p>document.write will erase body contents if the code snippet is loaded via AJAX</p>\n\n<p><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/a/2360112/208067">http://stackoverflow.com/a/2360112/208067</a></p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-03-10 21:10:08', '2012-03-11 17:17:58', '2012-03-11 17:17:58', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/151.diff'),
