(322, 0, 322, NULL, NULL, 'Fix problem with menus starting at level greater than 1.', '<p>See <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28843">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28843</a></p>', 3, 0, 1, '2012-08-22 22:03:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-22 22:03:58', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/322.diff'),
