(324, 0, 324, NULL, NULL, 'Make h2s go just around the title since this is semantically correct plus won''t break templates.', '<p>See <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28980">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28980</a></p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-23 13:25:58', '2012-08-30 06:18:46', '2012-08-30 06:18:46', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/324.diff'),
(325, 0, 325, NULL, NULL, 'Set default color in Isis options. Change spelling of color to colour.', '<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28983">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28983</a></p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-23 16:59:35', '2012-09-15 00:29:04', '2012-09-15 00:29:04', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/325.diff'),
(326, 0, 326, NULL, NULL, 'Remove non structural hrs from layouts', '<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28984">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28984</a></p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-23 20:51:49', '2012-08-26 09:34:53', '2012-08-26 09:34:54', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/326.diff'),
(327, 0, 327, NULL, NULL, 'class JFile not found', '<p>I''ve found a bug when you try to copy a template and are using cache handler diff from "file".</p>\n\n<p>the JFile class are not loaded and got a Fatal Error.</p>\n\n<p>Report trackert link in joomlacode.</p>\n\n<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28985">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28985</a></p>\n\n<p>Cheers,</p>\n\n<p>Julio Pontes</p>\n\n<p>Ps.: Need to check this on 1.5.X<br>\nPs.: This patch its only for 2.5.X series</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-23 22:31:47', '2012-08-26 09:57:52', '2012-08-26 09:57:52', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/327.diff'),
(328, 0, 328, NULL, NULL, 'Add default to captcha rule', '', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-24 02:49:47', '2012-08-25 04:19:16', '2012-08-25 04:19:23', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/328.diff'),
(329, 0, 329, NULL, NULL, 'debug language does''nt work', '<p>if debug language set to yes in the global configuration both back-end  and front-end of the site give blank pages with server error can connect to server.</p>\n\n<p>test environment ;</p>\n\n<p>wamp server under windows7</p>\n\n<p>Apache 2.2.22<br>\nPHP 5.3.13<br>\nMySQL 5.5.24</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-24 13:18:37', '2012-08-26 09:15:32', '2012-08-26 09:15:37', NULL),
(330, 0, 330, NULL, NULL, 'Unstyled hrs', '<p>Per issue <a href="https://github.com/JTracker/jissues/issues/60" class="issue-link" title="Remove luminous library, content plugin, and render markdown test page based on GitHub''s API">#60</a> at <a href="https://github.com/Joomla3-Admin-template/joomla-cms/issues/60" class="issue-link" title="Unstyled  hrs">Joomla3-Admin-template/joomla-cms#60</a>, removing hr elements being used for stylistic purposes</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-25 00:30:41', '2012-12-28 21:55:25', '2012-12-28 21:55:25', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/330.diff'),
(331, 0, 331, NULL, NULL, 'Make all content editing screens consistent and use new fields', '<p>All editing screens now share the same basic layout of article editing.<br>\nNew fields that were added to the sql are incorporated in backend editing.<br>\nThis replaces the previous pull request.</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-25 15:58:16', '2012-09-15 00:28:41', '2012-09-15 00:28:41', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/331.diff'),
(332, 0, 332, 28764, NULL, '[#28764] user notes category is not properly nested in the assets table', '<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28764">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28764</a></p>\n\n<p>This pull replaces pull 297. (<a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/297" class="issue-link" title="Usernotes3">joomla/joomla-cms#297</a>)</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-26 15:29:31', '2012-10-08 00:37:41', '2012-10-08 00:37:41', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/332.diff'),
(333, 0, 333, NULL, NULL, 'Fixed modules modChrome_html5 coding style. Added support not to use "span" at all', '<p>I fixed coding style of modules.php file as discussed here <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/GyZf9_LgDDU">https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/GyZf9_LgDDU</a></p>\n\n<p>Also implemented not to use "Bootstrap size" parameter at all, because adding "spanX" to a class sometimes spoils the output: <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/WACu4ymBd5o">https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/WACu4ymBd5o</a></p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-27 11:18:26', '2012-10-01 12:20:22', '2012-10-01 12:20:22', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/333.diff'),
(334, 0, 334, NULL, NULL, 'Usernotes4 25x', '<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28764">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28764</a></p>\n\n<p>Rebased.  Previous pull was <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/298" class="issue-link" title="Usernotes3 25x">joomla/joomla-cms#298</a>.</p>', 3, 0, 1, '2012-08-28 13:25:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-28 13:25:26', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/334.diff'),
(335, 0, 335, NULL, NULL, 'Fix JModel regex', '<p>The JModel regex that guesses option from model class name doesn''t take<br>\ninto account models that may end in the word "Model." ie: AutosModelModel</p>\n\n<p>This new regex fixes that.</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-28 15:07:40', '2012-12-29 06:16:53', '2012-12-29 06:16:53', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/335.diff'),
(336, 0, 336, NULL, NULL, 'Update media/editors/tinymce/jscripts/tiny_mce/tiny_mce.js', '<p>Problems inserting templates within tiny_mce led me to these two changes within her mceInsertContent &amp; parse functions</p>\n\n<p>Please tell me what''s wrong with my changes, as I assume this creates a security risk..<br><br>\nI tried various methods within Joomla! to set valid html elements, including:<br>\nGlobal Options -&gt; text filtering.. <br>\nin my form.xml</p>\n\n<div class="highlight"><pre>filter="raw"\n</pre></div>\n\n<p>This helped..<br>\nplugins/.../tinymce.php</p>\n\n<div class="highlight"><pre><span class="nv">$elements</span><span class="p">[]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">''p[*]''</span><span class="p">;</span>\n<span class="nv">$elements</span><span class="p">[]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">''a[*]''</span><span class="p">;</span>\n<span class="nv">$elements</span><span class="p">[]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">''div[*]''</span><span class="p">;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n<p>setContent() was never called within mceInsertContent, only setHTML().<br>\nIt appears to me that tinymce''s parse function is not comparing inserted elements with acceptable elements correctly.. thinking standard tags were invalid..  Also, stripping templates tags when serializing..</p>\n\n<p>Hopefully this leads to a proper solution..<br>\nPerhaps a newer version of tiny_mce solves this issue correctly.</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-28 22:20:13', '2012-08-29 03:26:20', '2012-08-29 18:13:31', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/336.diff'),
(337, 0, 337, NULL, NULL, 'Patch 1', '<p>inserting the "span" element to wrap the text of the "li" element when it does not have any link, so css styling is possible and easier</p>', 3, 0, 1, '2012-08-29 22:39:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-30 06:14:55', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/337.diff'),
(338, 0, 338, NULL, NULL, 'improving CSS styling possibilities of the pagebreaker navigation buttons/links', '<p>When articles got inserted "pagebreaks"  the content plugin "pagebreak" inserts at the bottom of the article a "ul" element with 2 navigation buttons "prev" and "next" just like this:</p>\n\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>Prev</li>\n  <li><a href="......">Next &gt;&gt;</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<p>As you people can see, when the user is at the first or last page, the navigation elements shows a "li" element with just text which makes hard does some CSS styling to that element, to solve this problem I propose the just wrap the content of the first and last navigation element with a "span" element</p>\n\n<p>the file to modify in question is <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/blob/master/plugins/content/pagebreak/pagebreak.php#L313">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/blob/master/plugins/content/pagebreak/pagebreak.php#L313</a></p>\n\n<p>line: 313 and 323</p>\n\n<p>With something like:</p>\n\n<p>$next = "" . JText::_(''JNEXT'') . "";</p>\n\n<p>and </p>\n\n<p>$prev = "" . JText::_(''JPREV'') . "";</p>\n\n<p>This change is minimum and doubt it will cause any kind of issue, and developers would be able to do some styles like this </p>\n\n<p>.pagination li span { //style for disable button }<br>\n.pagination li a { //style for enabled button }</p>\n\n<p>here is the pull request </p>\n\n<p><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/337" class="issue-link" title="Patch 1">joomla/joomla-cms#337</a></p>\n\n<p>I hope I''m doing this correctly</p>', 3, 0, 1, '2012-08-29 22:40:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-29 22:47:38', NULL),
(339, 0, 339, NULL, NULL, 'Remove logging of routine events from smart search adapter', '', 3, 0, 10, '2012-08-30 00:22:32', '2012-09-01 09:45:51', '2012-09-01 09:45:51', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/339.diff'),
