(379, 0, 379, NULL, NULL, 'Search form module template (html) fixed', '<p>Module Div should be on the outside of form not the inside, this helps users style their search forms properly. It is also more semantic.</p>\n\n<p>Does not affect current state/look. (backwards compatible)</p>', 3, 0, 10, '2012-09-14 22:26:38', '2012-09-15 10:23:27', '2012-09-15 10:23:27', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/379.diff'),
