(545, 0, 545, NULL, NULL, 'Fix "where" clause for query on table "updates": integer column "client_id", use "0" instead of ""', '<p>Fix "invalid input syntax for integer" (PostgreSQL)</p>\n\n<p>Tracker: <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_id=8103&amp;tracker_item_id=29680">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_id=8103&amp;tracker_item_id=29680</a></p>', 3, 0, 1, '2012-11-14 01:56:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-11-14 01:56:53', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/545.diff'),
