(3261229, 59, 'radiant-tech', '<p>Agree quote is not required as the modified and created dates are quoted during storage by JTable.</p>', '2011-12-23 14:17:24'),
(3263614, 61, 'realityking', '<p>Thanks for contributing :)</p>\n\n<p>This is a platform issue and should be dealt with there (<a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform</a>). It would be great if you could resubmit it there.</p>', '2011-12-23 18:52:18'),
(3264740, 61, 'janschoenherr', '<p>Thanks: <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/issues/672" class="issue-link" title="setting name via config array">joomla/joomla-platform#672</a></p>', '2011-12-23 21:12:25'),
