(4247910, 138, 'realityking', '<p>That''s because all patches still have to go trough the issue tracker (<a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemBrowse&amp;tracker_id=8103">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemBrowse&amp;tracker_id=8103</a>) for testing before they can be accepted. As infograf768 mentioned you need to open an issue there or your patch won''t be accepted.</p>\n\n<p>It''s not the most elegant system, but the github issue handling just doesn''t cut it for the project.</p>', '2012-02-29 22:10:09'),
