(4516699, 153, 'piotr-cz', '<p>Thanks for the fix.<br>\nActually I think the commit should go to Joomla Platform github repository (<a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform</a>).</p>\n\n<p>There was already an effort here: <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/issues/454" class="issue-link" title="Removed bug producing insert from JSessionStorageDatabase::write()">joomla/joomla-platform#454</a>, with tracker: <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=26956">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=26956</a></p>\n\n<p>I hope your commit will be accepted, this is a serious bug.</p>', '2012-03-15 10:02:36'),
(4522372, 101, 'oc666', '<p>IMHO, in addition to mbabker comment about doing this on 3.0 branch, I hope we''ll have some unit tests for 3.0 branch, what will make this change less risky (although is just code styling).</p>', '2012-03-15 15:49:16'),
