(4881650, 157, 'benjaminpick', '<p>Should be fixed there:<br><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28154">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28154</a></p>', '2012-04-02 16:02:21'),
(4891716, 157, 'okonomiyaki3000', '<p>Thanks. Now if only someone would fix Joomlacode itself. That site logs me out after practically any action (even clicking a link). </p>', '2012-04-03 00:03:36'),
