(6801768, 259, 'KISS-Web-Design', '<p>Cannot create new account on joomlacode, after recieving the confirmation email and clicking through to the ''finish the registration process'' page I enter my details and get a "Could not get user" error message.</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr>\n<p>From: infograf768 <a href="mailto:reply@reply.github.com">reply@reply.github.com</a><br>\nTo: Chris Jones-Gill <a href="mailto:chris.jones-gill@kisswebdesign.co.uk">chris.jones-gill@kisswebdesign.co.uk</a> <br>\nSent: Wednesday, 4 July 2012, 18:12<br>\nSubject: Re: [joomla-cms] remove obsolete img border from tinymce.php (deprecated in html4, obsolete in html5) (#259)</p>\n\n<p>Please post a new tracker on joomlacode and cross-reference here.</p>\n\n<hr>\n<p>Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub:<br><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/259#issuecomment-6764417" class="issue-link" title="remove obsolete img border from tinymce.php (deprecated in html4, obsolete in html5)">joomla/joomla-cms#259</a></p>\n</blockquote>', '2012-07-06 10:23:21'),
