(6961057, 276, 'realityking', '<p>These are PHP 5.4 related. Fix can be found here: <a href="https://github.com/realityking/joomla-cms/commit/a5c6176503af1afd353a0415d599a3bf24498a6d" class="commit-link">realityking/joomla-cms@<tt>a5c6176</tt></a></p>\n\n<p>I haven''t submitted them yet because I kept finding more of them and we should fix them in 2.5 as well.</p>', '2012-07-13 11:56:05'),
