(8020502, 306, 'elinw', '<p>merge</p>', '2012-08-25 05:47:24'),
(8020537, 300, 'elinw', '<p>This is an issue in the platform. Would you make a pull request for the change and explain why you think it is necessary in the platform repository?</p>', '2012-08-25 05:55:35'),
(8023504, 329, 'allrude', '<p>the joomla 3.0 Alpha 2 from the announcement, not the trunk</p>\n\n<p>Ruud van Zuidam<br>\nM  +*31-637170938*</p>\n\n<p>On Fri, Aug 24, 2012 at 6:19 PM, Rouven WeÃŸling <a href="mailto:notifications@github.com">notifications@github.com</a>wrote:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>What Joomla version did you use to test?</p>\n\n<p>â€”<br>\nReply to this email directly or view it on GitHub<a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/329#issuecomment-8007244" class="issue-link" title="debug language does''nt work">joomla/joomla-cms#329</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>', '2012-08-25 13:58:22'),
(8023528, 329, 'realityking', '<p>This should be fixed in current master. You can get a copy here: <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/zipball/master">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/zipball/master</a></p>\n\n<p>Please confirm whether it''s fixed or not.</p>', '2012-08-25 14:01:52'),
(8024089, 280, 'andreatarr', '<p>Tested on the alpha2 -- It works for the modals used in Hathor, but has no effect on Isis modals which I assume use different js.<br>\nI''d recommend committing to fix this issue with Hathor and to commit to 2.5 branch as well where it will fix both Hathor and Bluestork.</p>', '2012-08-25 15:03:54'),
(8031466, 329, 'allrude', '<p>I can confirm that the issue is fixed Rouven</p>\n\n<p>greetings</p>\n\n<p>Ruud van Zuidam<br>\nM  +*31-637170938*</p>\n\n<p>On Sat, Aug 25, 2012 at 4:01 PM, Rouven WeÃŸling <a href="mailto:notifications@github.com">notifications@github.com</a>wrote:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>This should be fixed in current master. You can get a copy here:<br><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/zipball/master">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/zipball/master</a></p>\n\n<p>Please confirm whether it''s fixed or not.</p>\n\n<p>â€”<br>\nReply to this email directly or view it on GitHub<a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/329#issuecomment-8023528" class="issue-link" title="debug language does''nt work">joomla/joomla-cms#329</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>', '2012-08-26 09:04:57'),
