(8186689, 162, 'nternetinspired', '<p>Thanks for this Matt, it bugs the hell out of me :)</p>', '2012-08-31 09:22:00'),
(8209387, 341, 'mbabker', '<p>With this, we also need to update <code>JAdministrator::getTemplate()</code> to not use Bluestork as the fallback template.  We also need to ensure the SQL files are updated to drop the extension and style records for new installs.  I''d do that as a separate patch so that the actual diff for those changes isn''t mixed in with 537 deleted files and is actually reviewable.</p>', '2012-09-01 02:41:00'),
