(8597580, 401, 'jneubauer', '<p>what''s the "standard" for using the badge for denoting hits and/or items?<br>\nsome views have them pushed over to the right using the pull-right class - some have them close to the text like the weblinks category view.</p>\n\n<p>I was looking at the weblinks category - seems that the subcategories should use the badge for denoting number of links to keep it in sync with other views - but if I send that to the right, it goes all the way over as opposed to the items above that are next to the title.</p>\n\n<p>I think though that if we''re going to start using the badge - we should use that across the board instead of the old # of links text</p>', '2012-09-16 18:45:15'),
