(8615306, 190, 'fititnt', '<p><a href="https://github.com/Jayflux" class="user-mention">@Jayflux</a> added a pull with just <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/190#commits-pushed-137d207" class="issue-link" title="[#28403] Validation error on com_finder">joomla/joomla-cms#190</a> on <a href="https://github.com/Jayflux/joomla-cms/commit/62bee6a50d506881ae120f541f798ba301ed4ec4" class="commit-link">Jayflux/joomla-cms@<tt>62bee6a</tt></a> that is now added to CMS.</p>\n\n<p>So validation problem is OK now. All other changes, that also require add javascript, I will think again later for or maybe just a plain javascript version or made also a jQuery version instead of just a Mootools.</p>\n\n<p>Thanks to everyone who participated in this pull.</p>', '2012-09-17 14:03:30'),
