(9784155, 518, 'fastnetwebdesign', '<p>That''s exactly what I do, but with an additional IE hack - it works great:</p>\n\n<p>.embed-container {<br>\n    position: relative;<br>\n    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16/9 ratio <em>/<br>\n    padding-top: 30px; /</em> IE workaround*/<br>\n    height: 0;<br>\n    overflow: hidden;<br>\n}<br>\n.embed-container iframe,<br>\n.embed-container object,<br>\n.embed-container embed {<br>\n    position: absolute;<br>\n    top: 0;<br>\n    left: 0;<br>\n    width: 100%;<br>\n    height: 100%;<br>\n}</p>', '2012-10-25 16:25:02'),
