(11805986, 618, 'ITPrism', '<p>I agree with you Jonathan. I see the discussion about Joomla! Articles ( com_content ) and onContentPrepare is not over. It will be great if we find a solution because that issue has been reported a year ago.</p>', '2013-01-02 11:58:55'),
