(11830868, 625, 'phproberto', '<p>The patch works fine but contains some trailing spaces:</p>\n\n<p><a target="_blank" href="https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/1119272/39680/586992cc-553c-11e2-975e-9d5d4b10dd29.png"><img src="https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/1119272/39680/586992cc-553c-11e2-975e-9d5d4b10dd29.png" alt="error-trailing" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>\n\n<p>I have the patch test ready. Ping me when fixed and I''ll post the test and mark the issue as ready to commit :)</p>', '2013-01-03 00:35:28'),
(11836159, 633, 'infograf768', '<p>Please create tracker on joomlacode.<br>\nAlso I suggest using same format as other similar code, i.e<br>\n.     $lang-&gt;load($component, JPATH_BASE, null, false, false)<br>\n||   $lang-&gt;load($component, JPATH_BASE, $lang-&gt;getDefault(), false, false)<br>\n||   etc.</p>', '2013-01-03 06:46:26'),
